snippet: Secretary of State John Kerry and Foreign Minister Elías Jaua got together during an Organization of American States session in Guatemala.
abstract: Secretary of State John Kerry meets with Venezuela's Foreign Min Elias Jaua, announcing start of talks aimed at improving relations between two countries.

byline.original: By WILLIAM NEUMAN and RANDAL C. ARCHIBOLD
byline.contributor: William Neuman reported from Caracas, and Randal C. Archibold from Antigua, Guatemala. María Eugenia Díaz contributed reporting from Caracas.

lead_paragraph: Secretary of State John Kerry and Foreign Minister Elías Jaua got together during an Organization of American States session in Guatemala.

headline.seo: Kerry Meets With Venezuelan Foreign Minister
headline.main: Kerry Meets With Official of Venezuela to Set Talks
headline.print_headline: Kerry Meets With Official Of Venezuela To Set Talks
